---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/SectionHeader.astro";
import ToolCard from "../components/ToolCard.astro";
import projects from "../data/projects.json";

import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

interface Project {
	name: string;
	description: string;
	url: string | null;
	github_url: string | null;
	image: string;
	status: string | null;
}
---

<Layout title="Isaac" hideFooter={false}>
	<main>
		<Header />

		<h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-3xl font-bold font-souvenir mb-4 mt-6">Hi, I'm Isaac &#128075;</h1>

		<p id="about">
			I'm a <span class="highlight">Programmer</span> with kids living out of Nigeria, and working by proxy from Sharjah. I enjoy <span class="highlight">building</span> things tailored for the hacking community just as much as I enjoy exploring different fields including mathematics, astrophysics, blockchain, USOil, other programming languages while doing that.
			<br />
			In between being a devoted dad and expressing intent to pursue a doctorate in applied mathematics, I <span class="highlight">experiment</span> a lot and build some really crazy stuffs and post about oil on <a href="https://x.com/1cbyc" class="text-violet-400" target="_blank">Twitter</a> from time to time); I find my family interesting and enjoy working on things that make hacking much easier these days, I also try to do <a href="/blog" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-500">a bit of writing</a> when I can
			to stroke my ego.
		</p>

		<section id="tools">
			<SectionHeader>Tools</SectionHeader>
			<p>
				My primary stack includes PHP, Erlang & Typescript. I have listed some of the languages/tools I have used and/or still use below; there are definitely a lot more but these are the ones I think are most relevant to showcase.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-5">
				<ToolCard name="Astro" local />
				<ToolCard name="React" local />
				<ToolCard name="TailwindCSS" local />
				<ToolCard name="PHP" local />
				<ToolCard name="Typescript" local />
				<ToolCard name="Erlang" local />
				<ToolCard name="Gleam" local />
				<ToolCard name="SQLite" local />
				<ToolCard name="MySQL" local />
				<ToolCard name="PostgreSQL" local />
				<ToolCard name="MongoDB" local />
				<ToolCard name="Redis" local />
				<ToolCard name="Git" local />
				<ToolCard name="Linux" local />
				<ToolCard name="Docker" local />
				<ToolCard name="NeoVim" local />
				<ToolCard name="RabbitMQ" local />
			</div>

			<div class="border border-neutral-500 rounded-lg p-4 mt-5">
				<p>-&gt; Other things I am currently learning, intend to take a deeper dive into or get started with at some point in the future</p>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-x-6 gap-y-5 mt-5">
					<ToolCard name="Swift" local />
					<ToolCard name="Rust" local />
					<ToolCard name="Kubernetes" local />
					<ToolCard name="SurrealDB" local />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="projects">
			<SectionHeader>Projects</SectionHeader>
			<p>
				During my free time, I like to build things that I find interesting and/or would use; sometimes to learn more about something or just to fix a problem that's particularly
				frustrated me enough at that point in time. Here are a couple of them, you can find other random things I build on my GitHub profile.
			</p>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-6 gap-y-8 lg:gap-8 mt-5">
				{
					(projects as Project[]).map((project) => (
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
							<div class="relative w-full border border-neutral-900 aspect-[1.5] overflow-hidden rounded-lg cursor-pointer">
								<img src={`/projects/${project.image}`} class="w-full h-full hover:scale-125 object-cover object-center transition-all" />
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-1 leading-none">{project.name}</h3>
							<p class="text-sm">{project.description}</p>
							<div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-auto">
								{project.status ? <div class="w-max bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-500 text-[10px] font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded drop-shadow-md">{project.status}</div> : <div />}
								<div class="flex gap-4 items-center lg:px-1">
									{project.url ? (
										<a href={project.url} target="_blank" class="block w-max text-xs font-medium">
											<i class="fa fa-external-link text-base" />
										</a>
									) : null}
									{project.github_url ? (
										<a href={"https://www." + project.github_url} target="_blank" class="block w-max text-xs font-medium">
											<i class="fa-brands fa-github text-lg" />
										</a>
									) : null}
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					))
				}
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
